Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:06.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,When watching "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.07,0:00:09.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,make sure you keep the room bright \Nand sit well away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.06,0:00:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll see you later, Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.82,0:00:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.13,0:00:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.34,0:00:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have time, go rent the DVDs \Nlisted here from Wataru's store.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.79,0:00:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold, so please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a problem! \NI have that taken care of!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.47,0:00:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.24,0:00:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What the? Where's the Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.32,0:00:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't turn around! \NI'll be directly in the wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.14,0:00:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're very resourceful, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.05,0:00:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Hinagiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.44,0:00:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? You're all spaced out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.27,0:00:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinagiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:00:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.49,0:01:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. There's \Nsomething on my mind, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.74,0:01:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.75,0:01:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that walking disaster \Nsprinkler of a superintendent
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.69,0:01:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has been up to no good again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.91,0:01:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that woman should \Nbe enjoying her vacation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on a tropical island right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.59,0:01:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are, Mistress Kuzuha. Say, "Ah!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But surely we didn't have to do \Nthe New Year's Breaking of the Mochi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.24,0:01:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all the way out here...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.15,0:01:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's for good luck, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.78,0:01:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then, what in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.28,0:01:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, my sis gave me New Year's money.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.57,0:01:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Katsura gave you New Year's money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.58,0:01:48.79,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,New Year's Money \N To Hinagiku From Sis
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.87,0:01:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She came over to the house yesterday \Nand left this on my desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.53,0:01:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it was just 500 yen in there, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.39,0:01:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,500 yen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.39,0:01:57.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:02:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's a fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.10,0:02:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I ever got every year \Nwas red beans or peanuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. You're going to be late \Nif you're too caught up in chitchat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're under arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, a knock to your noggin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.06,0:02:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She's not her usual self!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:21.40,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know, ladies and gentlemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:25.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That a humongous mansion like \Nthis exists somewhere in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.17,0:02:29.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The Miss's name is Nagi Sanzenin. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:33.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Her butler's name is Hayate Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:35.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,They are both a bit clueless
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:37.61,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and both have a bit of \Nthe wrong idea about each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.61,0:02:42.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but they share the immensely strong, \Nloving bond between servant and mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miss Katsura's acting \Ndifferently than usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.88,0:02:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's sparkling somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world happened, Sis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:50.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Zettai nante shinjinai!\N I don't believe in absolutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:53.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukanou nante nai! \NNo such thing as impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:59.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirai wa hiraku te no naka ni aru\N The future is in the open palm of my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:04.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Honne o misecha make datoka \NStuff like, showing your true feelings means defeat
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:09.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Dentaku hajiku jinsei datoka\N Or a life tapping away at a calculator
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:14.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kokoro o itsuwaru kurai nara\N Rather than be false to myself like that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:20.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichiten-battou baka-shoujiki mo kuuzen-zetsugo! \NI'll struggle to be uniquely naive and honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:25.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Komatta kao o mireba ki-ni-naru shi\N If I see a troubled look, I'll be concerned
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:30.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Jinsei isogu riyuu mo betsuni nai shi \NAnd it's not like I've got a reason to hurry through life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:36.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Takara no chizu wa kimi ni azukeyou \NI'll entrust you with the treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:42.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Juuou-mujin yori-michi datte tsukiau yo! \NI'll even keep you company on your free-ranging detours
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:45.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Rakkii-sugiru tenkai \NA development that's way too lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:48.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotae wa mayowanai \NI won't hesitate to give my answer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:53.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kantan sa! Subete wa kimi no tame ni \NIt's easy! It's all for you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:56.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuuhyou wa ki-ni-shinai \NI won't worry about the rumors
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:59.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Rettou-kan ni doujinai!\N I won't let a sense of inferiority get to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:04.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakedasu shunkan wa ima koko ni aru \NThe moment to start running is right here, right now
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despairing Goodbye to the Teacher \N~A Graduation Special
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.82,0:04:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not really anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but your Gigantor-esque change \Nin personality has us shocked...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you went \Nand ate some plants
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or maybe laughing mushrooms \Nfrom the side of the road?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why? Well, because...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.16,0:04:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that today is a very \Nspecial day for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A special day?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's almost time for the faculty \Nmorning meeting, so later!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.39,0:05:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katsy's quitting being a teacher?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that appears to be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.25,0:05:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that's just bananas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yujiki quitting being \Na teacher is inconceivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right. If she quit, \Nwhere would she live?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's clearly been \Nacting strangely since morning
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she said today was \Na special day or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of which, she even \Ngave Hinagiku New Year's money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps she plans to quit Hakuou \Nand go somewhere far away...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.41,0:05:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that turns out to be true, \NI'll shave my head bald!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll change my name to Spicysaltedcodroe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll change the title of this anime \Nto "Yamabiko the Combat Butler"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:51.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't change it without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, for example, if you actually \Nsaw her letter of resignation,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I'd be convinced.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:05:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:05:58.75,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Letter of Resignation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:02.34,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Letter of Resignation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined it could be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.41,0:06:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More like, if you found it, \Ntell us that first!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Katsy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Can I help you with something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the story about quitting true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a joke, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us it's a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, today's the last day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, it was just hard \Nto bring it up to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.26,0:06:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me it's not true, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! What's there to do \Nif not teaching?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of things to do out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Traveling, starting over in life...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:07:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Why did you keep quiet \Nabout such an important thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Don't be \Nsuch a stranger, Katsy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.76,0:07:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So true, so true, sauce true!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why wasn't there any discussion of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As an adult, there's no need \Nto discuss every little move like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Plenty of thought \Nwent into this decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Katsura!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about catching you \Nall unawares, but you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbyes have a way of suddenly \Nsneaking up on you one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sad, but life is full \Nof sudden goodbyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.59,0:07:38.72,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no dandelions in winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.45,0:07:47.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Marilla, I guess when you're \Ntruly sad, the tears just won't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sudden goodbyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in exchange, \NI'll never say goodbye to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Matthew, \Nbut I can't even must a single tear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:07:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See if I care about you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go die in some ditch somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hinagiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hina...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, let's go home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Awesome, huh? \NI got all this New Year's money!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, this was from Daddy. \NAnd this one's from Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was from Granny. \NAnd this one was Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:08:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:08:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I still hadn't \Ngiven you your New Year's money, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold out your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.01,0:09:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to let me off \Nwith that for this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in exchange, \NI'll never say goodbye to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, by all Maeda's Crackers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.31,0:09:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. I'll give you a piggyback ride, \Nso let's hurry on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.84,0:09:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, you liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oof, off we go.\N({\u1}Ru{\u0}kkorase t{\u1}to{\u0}.)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess ages trumps all.\N({\u1}To{\u0}shi ni wa katenai no {\u1}ne{\u0}.)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.17,0:10:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought Katsy would seriously quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem real.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When all's said and done, she's \Nbeen there for us in so many ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are we to survive the homework \Nassignments and tests from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This seems to have come as a great shock...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But something about this bugs me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.38,0:10:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.21,0:10:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She may be capricious, \Nbut this is on a whole another level.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps, but there's no disputing the facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish we could've had at least one \Nmore class of Katsy's world history.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:37.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:41.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,With the 6th period homeroom next, \Nit's goodbye Miss Katsura.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! Homeroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.89,0:10:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, then let's get homeroom started.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.22,0:10:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... um... Today's topic is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me! Miss Katsura!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:10:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's parts of the rise \Nand fall of the Frankish Empire
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I don't understand, so could \Nyou give us a lecture on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want an encore of the Reconquista \Nduring Spain's middle ages!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were the four apples \Nthat go down in history again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that Pythagoras \Nwas allergic to broad beans?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.37,0:11:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that the inventor \Nof instant curry was British?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:21.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We have lots of other questions, \Ntoo, so please teach it all to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.48,0:11:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's come to this, we better \Nfully enjoy Yukiji's final lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.44,0:11:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, are you listening? \NThis part is key. Key, I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1806, the Berlin Decree! \NMake sure you get that in your heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.04,0:11:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm, Miss Katsura's lectures always \Ndid move along at a good clip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems irresponsible, \Nbut she's actually a good teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, did you know \Nthat Napoleon was into fortune telling?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she teaches us stuff \Nthat's not in the textbooks, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a simple method, \Nwhere he held a coin in his left hand
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and flipped a crêpe in a frying pan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.12,0:12:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he did it five times \Nand he messed up on the fifth try.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.04,0:12:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the year 1812!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:06.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! The year he failed \Nin his invasion of Russia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess we'll never get to attend...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...these lectures again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it? This part is key, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.72,0:12:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you check it out \Nin your textbooks later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.15,0:12:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the reason Napoleon always has his \Nright hand in his pocket is because...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, wait. Why are you crying, Miss Segawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-These aren't tears! They're \Nleftover water from last night's bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.88,0:12:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so you guys finally understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That history is built \Non layers upon layers of tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.09,0:12:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saying hello and goodbye, \Nand then saying hello again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.86,0:12:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's those connections between \Npeople that make history!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kanji for "man" depicts two \Npeople leaning on each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:07.97,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Man
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Man cannot live life alone, you see!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't live...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...life alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.57,0:13:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once Sis is gone, I'll also...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't a soul out there \Nwho goes through life alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when people are apart, \Nin their hearts, they remain connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.96,0:13:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you all to understand that, too. \NAnd please don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tears are the sweat of the heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that love is the labor of the heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That concludes our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.11,0:14:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still lots more \Nthat we want to learn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And lots more fun we want to have!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:07.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without you, my life would be \Nin less danger and it'll be boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.84,0:14:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you all talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after all this, are you still \Ngoing to quit and leave us behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least stay with us until we graduate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that this was...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um, you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:29.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea you cared so much \Nabout me! It makes me so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Working as a teacher was a lot \Nharder than I ever imagined and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about this. We've \Ngot one more place to go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.08,0:14:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.63,0:14:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I handed my letter \Nof resignation to Miss Katsura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:14:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Letter of resignation?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.68,0:15:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean... this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh, sorry about that. \NI forgot to give it to the superintendent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Observing your lecture, \NI was able to realize something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.94,0:15:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To realize just how wonderful the bond \Nbetween teacher and student is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.94,0:15:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please forgive me \Nfor not seeing how deeply you love me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how touching this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, um, there's a huge storm \Nof "why" brewing here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're not quitting, Yukiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? There's no way I'd quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.34,0:15:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about that unnaturally \Nsparkling smiley aura from this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.76,0:15:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because today's been a super \Nlucky day for me since morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's Mistress Nobuko \NSaeki's fortune for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:16:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations! In first \Nplace come the Scorpios!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Particularly for those of you \Nwith blood type B, who love to drink,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.18,0:16:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and whose pinky toe nails are long,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.07,0:16:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this is a once in a dozen \Nyears super lucky day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if stuff like that's ever accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A l-lucky standing tea leaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.98,0:16:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The egg!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The eyebrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:18.03,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Rhapsody of the Koalas
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:19.58,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Choco-balls
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Red snappers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what happened! \NDon't you think it's amazing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uber happy! Super happy! \NI'm totally on a roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, look! These are the actual goods!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder even Napoleon \Nbelieved in fortune telling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.53,0:16:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For my stupid sister's numerous \Nmisleading, bothersome reactions,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am truly sorry \Nfor the trouble she's caused!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.17,0:16:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems we jumped to conclusions, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was strange from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did we cry all those tears for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make sure to get back at you for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Give us a free pass \Nfor 50 years' worth of homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What did I ever do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never going to \Nbelieve in fortunes again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:11.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And thus, the spinster teacher \Ngrew ever more dispirited.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.64,0:17:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what meaning was there in Miss \NKatsura giving you New Year's money?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.24,0:17:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That mystery's already been solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.59,0:17:27.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. Come at me with everything \Nyou got. You sons of bitches.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.93,0:17:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so utterly hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.52,0:17:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you real, proper \NNew Year's money someday, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.86,0:17:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When is someday?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.65,0:17:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, next year...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not quite sure I can make that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.44,0:17:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In three years...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.95,0:17:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err, well... In ten years...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get it to you for sure \Nby New Year's ten years from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:07.69,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Video Rental V Tachibana
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, "Pirates of Sanriku Coast" \Nand "Spider Guy 3", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.35,0:18:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Nagi to make sure she \Nreturns them by the due date.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.92,0:18:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, if you don't mind, \Nplease take this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:30.12,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Urusai People
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please think nothing of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My grandma sent me a massive shipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.49,0:18:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-These are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're still available?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.27,0:18:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, where in the world \Nis Saki's grandmother from...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New Year's card I wrote for Hayate...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been trying to decide \Nwhether to send it or not
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.15,0:18:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and now the New Year's here already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.03,0:18:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More like, didn't I decide \Nthat my resolution for this year
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was to become a mature woman, \Nbrimming with courage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:58.40,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year! Here's to another \Ngreat year! Ayumu Nishizawa
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it! I'll come again tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.13,0:19:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to pick a fight, bitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?! What should I do?! \NI think I might get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You listening?! \NI'll beat the crap outta you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:15.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mess with us and we'll get you good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:18.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Or actually, why do I always get \Ninto trouble like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:19.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some nerve tackling me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes, Miss Nishizawa, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is, right? Hayate's friend, as I recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were of great assistance last year \Nwhen you let Nagi stay the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.53,0:19:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you saw, she can be \Na difficult child in many ways,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I hope you'll continue \Nto be friends with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.70,0:19:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.45,0:19:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Who are these gentlemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.48,0:19:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.33,0:19:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why would you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.05,0:19:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just 'cause you're a maid \Nwith some cute looks,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you better not ignore us, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry. I don't understand Klingon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.87,0:20:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Japanese, ya moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You keep giving us lip
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.42,0:20:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you won't get away with it, \Nno matter how cute a maid you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a boorish man to suddenly attempt \Nto grab a woman by the collar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.01,0:20:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was just Xing Yi Quan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, I only know enough for self-defense
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's only useful \Nfor catching someone by surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not gonna get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would advise you against that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or getting injured will be \Nthe least of your worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.49,0:20:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.84,0:20:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you hurt in any way?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dropped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.03,0:20:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is n-n-nothing! Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.54,0:21:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will pray that this turns out to be \Na good year for you, Miss Nishizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.19,0:21:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes, if you'd like... Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.63,0:21:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:30.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"I want to become a woman like her \Nthis year," thought Miss Nishizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.66,0:21:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did anything unusual happen at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.43,0:21:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.09,0:21:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did anything happen during your day, Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.32,0:21:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing of particular \Nnote for me, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why is it? I suddenly have \Na craving for marshmallows.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:51.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, they will battle \Nagainst sine, cosine, and tangent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:22:06.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaretai fureraretetai\NI want to be loved, to feel that touch
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:11.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Motomeru bakari no kimochi wa\NThe sense of continually seeking
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:15.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hibi o kumoraseteta\NUsed to darken my days
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.35,0:22:23.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi ni deau sono hi made wa\NUntil the day I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:32.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Namae yonde sora ni hibiku-youni\NCall my name so it echoes to the skies
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.16,0:22:42.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayoi-michi mo kitto futari nara\NEven lost, with the two of us, surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.21,0:22:48.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsunaida te to te hanasanai\NI won't let go of your hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.97,0:22:51.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamoritainda\NI want to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:57.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Saa ikou bokura wa\NCome on, let's go, we'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:23:09.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ima o mitsumete aruki-hajimeru\N...look at the present and start walking
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:27.92,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiji Katsura's
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:27.92,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(217.037,279.75)} Lettering by Hitomi Nabatame
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.82,0:23:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiji Katsura's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.37,0:23:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Butler Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.53,0:23:30.22,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Butler Report
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.44,0:23:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! I'm the charming \Nfemale teacher, Yukiji Katsura.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.14,0:23:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, listen to this, everyone. \NMy character song's finally complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.88,0:23:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a bit nervous about \Nrecording for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.88,0:23:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I did my best for my fans!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.29,0:23:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sis, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.31,0:23:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hina, I didn't know you were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.81,0:23:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you didn't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.33,0:23:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing this segment together,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.12,0:23:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we even had a rehearsal \Nyesterday, remember?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.49,0:23:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.35,0:23:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, anyway, Hina even joins me \Non the second song on the disc,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.90,0:23:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so please make sure you get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.43,0:23:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the royalty's all mine, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.89,0:23:56.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.41,0:23:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,224)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.42,0:23:59.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't he have any weaknesses or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.41,0:24:00.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Weaknesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.41,0:24:20.22,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(174,307)}The next episode of \N"Hayate the Combat Butler" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.58,0:24:02.60,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,For the heroes of manga and anime,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.60,0:24:04.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,they tend to come with \Nweaknesses by default, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.96,0:24:06.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Is that how it works?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.75,0:24:08.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The butler-in-debt's weakness, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.29,0:24:09.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.67,0:24:12.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys like him sometimes have \Nthe most unexpected weaknesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.78,0:24:16.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Like a Dog, \Na Mouse and a Bulldog".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.09,0:24:17.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.92,0:24:19.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.37,0:24:20.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.22,0:24:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a Dog, a Mouse, and a Bulldog
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.22,0:24:24.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Borg Get On to "Hayate \Nthe Combat Butler" again next time!
